actions.text: Reported to Senate from the Committee on Rules and Administration, S. Rept. 93-647.

official_title: A resolution authorizing the printing of the Seventy-fifth Annual Report of the National Society of the Daughters of the American Revolution as a Senate document.

summary.text: Provides that the Seventy-fifth Annual Report of the National Society of the Daughters of the American Revolution for the year ended March 1, 1972, be printed, with an illustration, as a Senate document.

titles.title: A resolution authorizing the printing of the Seventy-fifth Annual Report of the National Society of the Daughters of the American Revolution as a Senate document.
